n=== Games played with 42 cards ===\nShortened Tarock pack:\n* [[Hungarian Tarock]]\n\n=== Games played with 48 cards ===\nGerman pack or French pack (2 packs each of 4 suits of 6 cards):\n* [[Binokel]]\n* [[Doppelkopf]]\n* [[Gaigel]]\n\n=== Games played with 52 cards ===\nFrench pack (Poker/Bridge) or Anglo-American pack (Poker): (4 suits of 13 cards)\n* [[Badugi]]\n* [[Barbu (card game)|Barbu]]\n* [[Battle (card game)|Battle]] or Battle Royal\n* [[Belle, Fluss and Einunddrei\u00dfig]]\n* [[Bridge (card game)|Bridge]]\n* [[Hearts (card game)|Hearts]]<ref>http://www.pagat.com/de/reverse/hearts.html</ref>\n* [[King (card game)|King]]\n* [[Poker]]\n* [[Whist]]\n\n=== Games played with 54 cards ===\n[[Tarot card games|Tarot/Tarock pack]] shortened to 21 trump cards, Fool and 4 suits of 8 cards:\n* [[Cego]]\n* [[Dreiertarock]]\n* [[Illustrated Tarock]]\n* [[K\u00f6nigrufen]]\n* [[Neunzehnerrufen]]\n* [[Point Tarock]]\n* [[Strohmandeln]]\n* [[Tapp Tarock]]\n\n=== Games played with 58 cards ===\nFrench pack (Zwicker): (4 suits of 13 cards and 6 Jokers) \n* [[Zwicker (card game)|Zwicker]]\n\n=== Games played with 62 cards ===\n78-card Swiss 1JJ Tarot pack minus the 1-4 of Swords and Batons and 7-10 of Cups and Coins:\n* [[Troggu]]\n\n=== Games played with 66 cards ===\n78-card French-suited tarot pack minus the 3 lowest cards of each suit:\n* [[Droggn]]\n\n=== Games played with 78 cards ===\nTarot/Tarock pack (21 trumps, Fool and 4 suits of 14 cards):\n* [[French Tarot]]\n* [[Gro\u00dftarock]]\n* [[Scarto]]\n* [[Troccas]]\n\n=== Games played with 97 cards ===\nMinchiate pack (40 trumps, Fool and 4 suits of 14 cards):\n* [[Minchiate]]\n\n=== Games played with 104 cards ===\nFrench pack (Poker/Bridge): 2 packs of 52 cards:\n* [[Zank-Patience|Spite and Malice]]\n\n=== Games played with 108 cards ===\nFrench pack (Canasta): 2 packs of 52 cards and 4 Jokers:\n* [[Canasta]]\n\n=== Games played with 110 cards ===\nFrench pack (Romm\u00e9): 2 packs of 52 cards and 6 Jokers:\n* [[Romm\u00e9]]\n\n=== Games played with 312 cards ===\n(6 packs of 52 cards)\n* [[Baccara (gambling game)|Baccara]]\n* [[Blackjack]]\n\n== Games played with proprietary packs - no additional equipment ==\n=== Games played with 31 cards ===\n* [[Schwarzer Peter (card game)|Schwarzer Peter]] (variant: 2 \u00d7 15 pairs, 1 Schwarzer Peter)\n\n=== Games played with 37 cards ===\n* [[Schwarzer Peter (card game)|Schwarzer Peter]] (variant: 2 \u00d7 18 pairs, 1 Schwarzer Peter)\n\n* [[Tichu]] (4 suits of 13 cards, 4 special cards)\n\n=== Games played with 60 cards ===\n* [[Wizard (card game)|Wizard]] (4 suits of 13 cards, 8 special cards)\n\n=== Games played with 80 cards ===\n* [[The Great Dalmuti]] (78 number cards, 2 Jokers)\n* [[Elfer Raus]] (4 suits of 20 cards)\n\n=== Games played with 81 cards ===\n* [[Set (card game)|Set]]\n\n=== Games played with 108 cards ===\n* [[Uno (card game)|Uno]]\n\n=== Games played with 160 cards ===\n* [[Ligretto]]\n\n=== Games played with 162 cards ===\n* [[Skip-Bo]]\n\n=== Games played with 500 cards ===\n* [[Dominion (card game)|Dominion]]\n\n== Games played with proprietary packs - additional equipment ==\n=== Games played with 16 cards ===\n* [[Love Letter (card game)|Love Letter]]\n\n=== Games played with 55 cards ===\n* [[Jaipur (card game)|Jaipur]]\n\n=== Games played with 60 cards ===\n* [[Hanabi (card game)|Hanabi]]\n\n=== Games played with 63 cards ===\n* [[Caylus Magna Carta]]\n\n=== Games played with 66 cards ===\n* [[23 (card game)|23]]<ref>http://www.amigo-spiele.de/spielregeln</ref> (number cards 1\u201323 in quantity of their value (1x1, 2x2 \u2026 23x23), 12 bonus chips, 50 penalty chips)\n\n=== Games played with 157 cards ===\n* [[7 Wonders (board game)|7 Wonders]]\n\n=== Games played with 160 cards ===\n* [[Race for the Galaxy]]\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n[[Category:card games|+]]\n[[Category:Lists of games|Card games sorted by number of cards]]\n", "name_user": "Wbm1058", "label": "safe", "comment": "Spelling co